{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "More than 10,000 Dutch companies will soon have to meet the requirements of the NIS2 directive. But the consequences are not limited to this group. An estimated 50,000 suppliers, from IT partners to cleaning companies, are also affected. This makes the role of purchasing and supply chain managers more important than ever.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "Every supplier in the chain can pose a potential risk. A weak link can lead to service disruptions, reputational damage or legal consequences. Purchasing and supply chain managers are therefore indispensable in identifying, discussing and managing cybersecurity risks within the entire chain. This requires sharpness, cooperation and expert knowledge. But luckily you don't have to do it alone.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "## Especially for purchasing professionals: six practical videos", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "The cyber platform Samen Digitaal Veilig developed six practical [videos] (https://samendigitaalveilig.nl/inkoop/) especially for purchasing professionals. The videos focus on the daily practice of purchasing and supply chain managers.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "- What the role of purchasing is within NIS2\n- How to recognize risks with suppliers\n- How to make suppliers aware of their responsibility\n- How to collaborate effectively with IT and legal colleagues\n- What tools are available for a smooth implementation\n- Why the NIS2 Quality Mark is an accessible alternative for tough ISO processes", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) and reduce your cyber risks.\n- View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars on our [Safe entrepreneurship page](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link).\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers", "source_title": "NIS2: crucial role for purchasing and supply chain managers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/NIS2-cruciale-rol-voor-inkoop-en-supply-chain-managers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 13, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
